  "2228030": {
    "name": "Dr. Fetus' Mean Meat Machine",
    "steam_appid": 2228030,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/6ec11ea933d7388bfd715acb42cc7e9b.poster.avif?t=1717679134\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/6ec11ea933d7388bfd715acb42cc7e9b.webm?t=1717679134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/6ec11ea933d7388bfd715acb42cc7e9b.mp4?t=1717679134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Dr. Fetus’ Mean Meat Machine》将经典解谜游戏玩法与《Super Meat Boy》的硬核平台元素完美结合。人工搭建的精美世界中包含 100 多个解谜关卡，充满极富创造力的陷阱和危机。在每个世界的尽头，都要准备好迎接一场终极 boss 战。<br><br>重温前作熟悉的场景，如画的森林、医院，还有 Puyo Puyo 风格的盐厂，克服挑战不断前进。不过在本作中，将 4 个同类克隆体凑到一起打出强力连击远远不够——还必须避开致命的危险和陷阱，如锯片、火箭和钟摆。本作在你熟悉喜爱的经典解谜游戏配方中添加了更多疯狂和硬核！<br><br>享受来自前作美术师的炫目背景和动画，聆听 RIDICULON 的美妙配乐，包含《Super Meat Boy Forever》独特混音和全新曲调。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/132fca62a3bd2d8172e620187e2ff6ac.poster.avif?t=1717679134\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/132fca62a3bd2d8172e620187e2ff6ac.webm?t=1717679134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/132fca62a3bd2d8172e620187e2ff6ac.mp4?t=1717679134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/d83ca1fc20a9844d1c6651086472ef35.avif?t=1717679134\" width=620 height=93 /></span><br>《Dr. Fetus’ Mean Meat Machine》紧接发生在《Super Meat Boy Forever》的故事之后。在对 Meat Boy 进行细致分析后（注意到关卡中的摄像头了吗？？），邪恶的 Dr. Fetus 拥有了创造 Meat Boy 完美克隆体所需的全部数据！只有一个问题：他收集的 DNA 样本并不完美，反过来又会产生一些……不完美的克隆……<br><br>但别担心，Dr. Fetus 知道如何解决。他建了一堆残酷的测试间，把所有克隆体扔进去，优胜劣汰。这些样本起初看来一点也不像 Meat Boy，但随着时间的推移，Dr. Fetus 痛恨的那张怪诞可爱的脸开始出现，完美的克隆即将诞生。目标达成之后……谁知道接下来会发生什么？说不定会折磨和杀害 Meat Boy 们取乐！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/6dfac91afa2a70ecca9fcb3f72c5bac3.poster.avif?t=1717679134\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/6dfac91afa2a70ecca9fcb3f72c5bac3.webm?t=1717679134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/6dfac91afa2a70ecca9fcb3f72c5bac3.mp4?t=1717679134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/5322d9aca2ae01d13885994b49b5b955.avif?t=1717679134\" width=620 height=93 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过 100 个人工制作的关卡，充满独特又致命的陷阱<br></li><li>增加了额外机制的超难 boss 战<br></li><li>解谜游戏和动作游戏的独特结合<br></li><li>协助 Dr. Fetus 创造完美的 Super Meat Boy 克隆体<br></li><li>重温《Super Meat Boy》和《Super Meat Boy Forever》的世界<br></li><li>由 RIDICULON 创作原声配乐，其中包含《Super Meat Boy Forever》独特混音和全新曲调<br></li><li>Team Meat 与《Super Meat Boy》原班美术联合开发<br></li><li>30 个成就等你解锁，挑战技术极限</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/74f85a441d49c588a4b3bc50cfba760c.poster.avif?t=1717679134\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/74f85a441d49c588a4b3bc50cfba760c.webm?t=1717679134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228030/extras/74f85a441d49c588a4b3bc50cfba760c.mp4?t=1717679134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
